{"tid":2148422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"過百警員到壹傳媒總部　集團通知員工突發狀況暫不上班","createTime":"2020-08-10T02:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T02:35:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f674452a6c777cfc353a0ee1cf28c9743dc92a97","tid":2148422,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:30:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542810-20200810.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542810-20200810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=677c7738\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542810-20200810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=32af5d90\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542810-20200810.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n消息指，壹傳媒創辦人黎智英涉嫌違反《港區國安法》勾結外國或境外勢力罪被捕，他早上乘坐警方7人車抵達九龍城警署，同一輛車早上10時許離開警署。另外，過百名警員進入壹傳媒將軍澳工業邨總部調查，集團通知員工不用上班。<br />\n<br />\n集團向員工發通知，指將軍澳辦公室有突發狀況，暫時不要上班，在途中的同事即時折返。<br />\n<br />\n集團又表示，穿梭巴士將因應要求暫停來回將軍澳廠房至調景嶺的服務，已經上班的同事需留在座位工作，等候下一步指示。"},{"pid":"343954dae58f17a3bc682619287e162d1011e10e","tid":2148422,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104f46c8248582cb724f4a4dfa07ee83ed9a0e3b","tid":2148422,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:32:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5e8e4503b213767f640644565d1ee42d83583c6","tid":2148422,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:35:14.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737770a9ce88dd8aeddc3fe06e7315ba46857c03","tid":2148422,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:35:52.000Z","msg":"WFH<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}